                            <comment id="17439409" author="tilman" created="Fri, 5 Nov 2021 18:05:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting this. I suspect that in your file a shading is done immediately after another shading, or at as the first operation. Because these were the two occurrences where the clip might be null. I have fixed the second one too, although it has no effect on test files.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
